1
00:00:02,836 --> 00:00:04,505
[ TINKLING, DOORBELL RINGS ]

2
00:00:04,538 --> 00:00:05,739
SO SORRY, FLUTTERSHY.

3
00:00:05,773 --> 00:00:08,509
I HATE BEING LATE
FOR OUR WEEKLY GET-TOGETHER.

4
00:00:08,542 --> 00:00:09,510
THE USUAL.

5
00:00:09,543 --> 00:00:11,112
[ ZIP! ]

6
00:00:11,145 --> 00:00:12,113
[ STEAM HISSING ]

7
00:00:12,146 --> 00:00:14,282
BUT YOU WOULD NOT BELIEVE
WHAT HAPPENED TO ME!

8
00:00:14,315 --> 00:00:16,117
IS EVERYTHING
ALL RIGHT?

9
00:00:16,150 --> 00:00:18,319
OH, IT'S MUCH MORE
THAN ALL RIGHT.

10
00:00:18,352 --> 00:00:21,522
I WAS ON MY WAY HERE
WEARING MY LATEST HAT CREATION,

11
00:00:21,555 --> 00:00:25,626
WHEN WHO SHOULD STOP ME
ON THE STREET BUT PHOTO FINISH!

12
00:00:25,659 --> 00:00:27,661
PHOTO FINISH?

13
00:00:29,163 --> 00:00:31,299
SHE'S THE MOST FAMOUS
FASHION PHOTOGRAPHER

14
00:00:31,332 --> 00:00:32,433
IN ALL OF EQUESTRIA!

15
00:00:34,602 --> 00:00:36,570
ANYHOO, SHE SAW MY HAT

16
00:00:36,604 --> 00:00:40,208
AND SAID IT WAS
"ABSOLUTELY MARVELOUS!"

17
00:00:40,241 --> 00:00:42,443
WHAT A LOVELY COMPLIMENT.

18
00:00:42,476 --> 00:00:43,511
SHE WAS SO IMPRESSED

19
00:00:43,544 --> 00:00:46,447
THAT SHE WANTS TO TAKE
SOME PICTURES AT MY SHOP,

20
00:00:46,480 --> 00:00:48,316
FEATURING
SOME OF MY CLOTHES!

21
00:00:48,349 --> 00:00:49,317
[ ZIP! ZIP! ]

22
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:51,385
THAT'S WONDERFUL.

23
00:00:51,419 --> 00:00:54,555
[ Shakily ] DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THIS COULD MEAN

24
00:00:54,588 --> 00:00:56,424
FOR MY FASHION CAREER?

25
00:00:56,457 --> 00:00:59,493
OH, RARITY,
I'M SO HAPPY FOR YOU.

26
00:00:59,527 --> 00:01:03,297
BUT I'M GOING TO NEED SOMEPONY
FABULOUS TO MODEL FOR ME.

27
00:01:03,331 --> 00:01:05,133
SOMEPONY WITH BEAUTY,

28
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:06,700
SOMEPONY WITH GRACE,

29
00:01:06,734 --> 00:01:08,169
SOMEPONY...

30
00:01:08,202 --> 00:01:09,570
LIKE YOU?

31
00:01:09,603 --> 00:01:11,772
OH, GOODNESS.
I DON'T KNOW.

32
00:01:11,805 --> 00:01:14,608
OH, THIS IS
SUCH A HUGE OPPORTUNITY,

33
00:01:14,642 --> 00:01:17,278
AND IT WOULD MEAN
SO MUCH TO ME.

34
00:01:17,311 --> 00:01:19,180
I'M FLATTERED, REALLY.

35
00:01:19,213 --> 00:01:21,849
NOPONY IS GOING TO HAVE
YOUR ELEGANCE AND POISE.

36
00:01:21,882 --> 00:01:23,451
BUT --
NOPONY.

37
00:01:23,484 --> 00:01:25,653
THERE HAS TO BE SOMEPONY
MORE QUALIF--
PLEASE?!

38
00:01:25,686 --> 00:01:27,455
SOMEPONY
MORE INTO FASHION.
PLEASE?!

39
00:01:27,488 --> 00:01:29,523
SOMEPONY MORE COMFORTABLE
IN THE SPOTLIGHT.

40
00:01:29,557 --> 00:01:31,859
PLEASE, PLEASE,
PLE-E-E-ASE?!

41
00:01:31,892 --> 00:01:33,761
[ TING! ]

42
00:01:33,794 --> 00:01:37,565
OH, IF IT'S THAT IMPORTANT
TO YOU, OF COURSE I'LL DO IT.

43
00:01:37,598 --> 00:01:40,468
[ GASPS ] OH, THANK YOU!
THANK YOU! THANK YOU! THANK YOU!

44
00:01:40,501 --> 00:01:42,836
YOU ARE THE BEST FRIEND
A PONY COULD EVER HAVE!

45
00:01:43,837 --> 00:01:48,209
[ SIGHS ] WHAT A WONDERFUL WAY
TO SPEND AN AFTERNOON.

46
00:01:48,242 --> 00:01:49,443
ISN'T IT?

47
00:01:49,477 --> 00:01:52,246
THOUGH, I WAS SO AFRAID YOU
WOULDN'T AGREE TO MODEL FOR ME

48
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,747
THAT I FELT
COMPLETELY FRAZZLED!

49
00:01:53,781 --> 00:01:55,483
I THINK I FEEL A PIMPLE
COMING ON.

50
00:01:55,516 --> 00:01:57,585
OH!
ONLY ONE SOLUTION.

51
00:01:57,618 --> 00:01:58,752
[ TINKLING ]

52
00:01:58,786 --> 00:02:00,654
THE USUAL.

53
00:02:01,855 --> 00:02:04,325
* MY LITTLE PONY

54
00:02:04,358 --> 00:02:06,160
* MY LITTLE PONY

55
00:02:06,194 --> 00:02:07,895
* AH-AH-AH-AH

56
00:02:07,928 --> 00:02:10,164
* MY LITTLE PONY

57
00:02:10,198 --> 00:02:12,500
* I USED TO WONDER
WHAT FRIENDSHIP COULD BE *

58
00:02:12,533 --> 00:02:14,235
* MY LITTLE PONY

59
00:02:14,268 --> 00:02:16,837
* UNTIL YOU ALL SHARED
ITS MAGIC WITH ME *

60
00:02:16,870 --> 00:02:18,872
* BIG ADVENTURE
* TONS OF FUN

61
00:02:18,906 --> 00:02:21,209
* A BEAUTIFUL HEART
FAITHFUL AND STRONG *

62
00:02:21,242 --> 00:02:22,676
* SHARING KINDNESS
* IT'S AN EASY FEAT

63
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,945
* AND MAGIC
MAKES IT ALL COMPLETE *

64
00:02:24,978 --> 00:02:28,516
* YEAH, MY LITTLE PONY

65
00:02:28,549 --> 00:02:35,556
* DO YOU KNOW YOU'RE ALL
MY VERY BEST FRIENDS? *

66
00:02:41,262 --> 00:02:43,864
HMM. SHE'S GOING TO WANT TO SEE
ATTITUDE AND PIZZAZZ.

67
00:02:43,897 --> 00:02:46,534
A-A-ATTITUDE AND...
PIZZAZZ.

68
00:02:46,567 --> 00:02:49,337
MORE LIGHT! IT HAS TO CATCH
THE SEQUINS JUST SO

69
00:02:49,370 --> 00:02:51,605
[ TINKLING ]
OR THE WHOLE OUTFIT
IS JUST A DISASTER.

70
00:02:51,639 --> 00:02:54,308
OOH, AND THE HEADDRESS
NEEDS MORE FEATHERS.

71
00:02:54,342 --> 00:02:55,909
PINKIE PIE,
MORE FEATHERS!

72
00:02:55,943 --> 00:02:57,878
[ SPROING! SPROING! SPROING! ]

73
00:02:57,911 --> 00:02:59,647
[ TINKLING ]

74
00:03:01,482 --> 00:03:02,250
[ POP! ]

75
00:03:02,283 --> 00:03:04,918
[ GASPS ] AND SEQUINS!
MORE SEQUINS!

76
00:03:06,487 --> 00:03:08,922
[ TINKLING ]

77
00:03:08,956 --> 00:03:10,391
[ WINCES ]

78
00:03:11,725 --> 00:03:12,793
AND MORE RIBBON!

79
00:03:12,826 --> 00:03:13,827
[ ZIP! ]

80
00:03:13,861 --> 00:03:15,863
OH, NO. LESS RIBBON.

81
00:03:15,896 --> 00:03:17,431
NO! MORE RIBBON.

82
00:03:17,465 --> 00:03:19,300
[ WINCES ]

83
00:03:21,269 --> 00:03:23,337
OH, THIS HEM
IS COMPLETELY OFF.

84
00:03:23,371 --> 00:03:24,338
PIN CUSHION!

85
00:03:24,372 --> 00:03:25,339
[ ZIP! ]

86
00:03:25,373 --> 00:03:26,640
[ WHOOSH! ]

87
00:03:26,674 --> 00:03:28,276
[ TINKLING ]

88
00:03:30,844 --> 00:03:32,813
THANK YOU ALL
FOR HELPING ME.

89
00:03:32,846 --> 00:03:36,784
I'M SORRY TO BE SO SHORT WITH
YOU, BUT I'M JUST SO NERVOUS.

90
00:03:36,817 --> 00:03:39,019
OOH,
DOESN'T THAT HURT?

91
00:03:39,052 --> 00:03:42,022
THICK SCALES.
CAN'T FEEL A THING.

92
00:03:42,055 --> 00:03:43,857
AND EVEN IF I COULD,

93
00:03:43,891 --> 00:03:46,860
THERE IS NO PAIN THAT WOULD
KEEP ME FROM ASSISTING...

94
00:03:46,894 --> 00:03:50,398
THE MOST BEAUTIFUL CREATURE
IN THE WORLD.

95
00:03:50,431 --> 00:03:52,266
UGH!

96
00:03:52,300 --> 00:03:53,801
I'M GONNA TELL YOU TWO
A SECRET,

97
00:03:53,834 --> 00:03:55,903
BUT YOU HAVE TO PROMISE
NOT TO TELL ANYONE.

98
00:03:55,936 --> 00:03:56,904
I PROMISE.

99
00:03:56,937 --> 00:03:58,806
CROSS MY HEART
AND HOPE TO FLY.

100
00:03:58,839 --> 00:04:00,474
STICK A CUPCAKE
IN MY EYE.

101
00:04:08,416 --> 00:04:11,552
I have a crush
on Rarity.

102
00:04:11,585 --> 00:04:12,953
[ GASPS ]

103
00:04:12,986 --> 00:04:14,822
WE WON'T SAY A WORD.

104
00:04:14,855 --> 00:04:15,623
GIVE ME A BREAK.

105
00:04:15,656 --> 00:04:17,558
EVERYPONY ALREADY KNOWS
HOW YOU --

106
00:04:17,591 --> 00:04:19,927
TWILIGHT! YOU PROMISED SPIKE
YOU WOULDN'T SAY ANYTHING.

107
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:22,296
HE TRUSTS YOU,
AND LOSING A FRIEND'S TRUST

108
00:04:22,330 --> 00:04:24,565
IS THE FASTEST WAY
TO LOSE A FRIEND FOREVER!

109
00:04:24,598 --> 00:04:25,633
BUT --

110
00:04:25,666 --> 00:04:28,402
FOREVE-E-E-R!

111
00:04:28,436 --> 00:04:29,537
MY LIPS ARE SEALED.

112
00:04:29,570 --> 00:04:30,771
THOUGH I'M PRETTY SURE

113
00:04:30,804 --> 00:04:33,341
RARITY IS GONNA PICK UP
ON YOUR FEELINGS.

114
00:04:35,376 --> 00:04:36,944
[ DOOR OPENS, BELL JINGLES ]

115
00:04:36,977 --> 00:04:39,513
[ Foreign accent ]
I, PHOTO FINISH...

116
00:04:39,547 --> 00:04:41,882
HAVE AWWIVED.

117
00:04:41,915 --> 00:04:44,618
LET ME JUST SAY,
WHAT AN HONOR.

118
00:04:46,620 --> 00:04:47,788
WE BEGIN...

119
00:04:47,821 --> 00:04:48,922
[ BOING! ]

120
00:04:48,956 --> 00:04:49,957
...NOW.

121
00:04:51,124 --> 00:04:53,927
ATTITUDE AND PIZZAZZ!

122
00:04:53,961 --> 00:04:56,497
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKING ]

123
00:04:56,530 --> 00:04:59,633
YES! SHOW PHOTO FINISH
SOMETHING!

124
00:04:59,667 --> 00:05:00,634
NO!

125
00:05:00,668 --> 00:05:02,503
[ WHIMPERS ]

126
00:05:02,536 --> 00:05:03,837
YES.

127
00:05:03,871 --> 00:05:05,806
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

128
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:07,508
[ TING! ]

129
00:05:07,541 --> 00:05:08,976
NO!

130
00:05:09,009 --> 00:05:10,778
YES.
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]

131
00:05:14,848 --> 00:05:16,550
NO!

132
00:05:16,584 --> 00:05:18,652
YES.

133
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,489
ENOUGH!

134
00:05:26,594 --> 00:05:29,397
SHE HARDLY TOOK
ANY PICTURES.

135
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,764
[ TINKLING ]

136
00:05:30,798 --> 00:05:34,768
I'M SO SORRY.
I TRIED MY BEST.

137
00:05:34,802 --> 00:05:36,637
WELL, THE HEADDRESS
IS TOO BIG FOR YOU,

138
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:37,971
AND THE CAPE
HAD TOO MUCH SPARKLE.

139
00:05:38,005 --> 00:05:41,375
I CAN'T BELIEVE I EVER THOUGHT
I COULD IMPRESS HER.

140
00:05:41,409 --> 00:05:43,143
IT SEEMS THAT I,
PHOTO FINISH,

141
00:05:43,176 --> 00:05:46,079
HAVE FOUND THE NEXT FASHION STAR
HERE IN PONYVILLE.

142
00:05:46,113 --> 00:05:47,481
REALLY?

143
00:05:47,515 --> 00:05:48,782
YES, REALLY.

144
00:05:48,816 --> 00:05:50,818
AND I, PHOTO FINISH,

145
00:05:50,851 --> 00:05:55,689
AM GOING TO HELP HER TO SHINE
ALL OVER EQVESTRIA!

146
00:05:57,157 --> 00:06:00,961
TOMORROW,
A PHOTO SHOOT IN ZE PARK!

147
00:06:00,994 --> 00:06:01,962
I GO!

148
00:06:01,995 --> 00:06:03,464
[ ZIP! ]

149
00:06:04,097 --> 00:06:05,699
DID YOU HEAR THAT?

150
00:06:05,733 --> 00:06:09,069
I AM GOING TO
"SHINE ALL OVER EQUESTRIA!"

151
00:06:09,102 --> 00:06:12,640
OH, RARITY, I WAS SO WORRIED
I'D RUINED EVERYTHING.

152
00:06:12,673 --> 00:06:16,577
OH, NEVER.
I KNEW YOU'D BE PERFECT.

153
00:06:16,610 --> 00:06:19,012
[ SQUEALING AND LAUGHING ]

154
00:06:19,046 --> 00:06:21,048
[ BOING! BOING! BOING! BOING! ]

155
00:06:29,723 --> 00:06:31,825
NO. NO. NO.

156
00:06:31,859 --> 00:06:32,960
YES!

157
00:06:32,993 --> 00:06:34,127
[ TINKLING ]

158
00:06:34,161 --> 00:06:36,764
THAT IS DEFINITELY
THE ONE.

159
00:06:36,797 --> 00:06:38,766
PHOTO FINISH
IS GOING TO LOVE IT.

160
00:06:38,799 --> 00:06:41,168
EVERYPONY
IS GOING TO LOVE IT!

161
00:06:41,201 --> 00:06:43,103
OH, I AM SO EXCITED
FOR YOU.

162
00:06:43,136 --> 00:06:45,506
JUST DON'T FORGET
US LITTLE PONIES

163
00:06:45,539 --> 00:06:49,042
WHEN YOU BECOME THE MOST FAMOUS
DESIGNER IN ALL OF EQUESTRIA.

164
00:06:49,076 --> 00:06:50,043
NEVER.

165
00:06:50,077 --> 00:06:51,779
Photo Finish:
PUT ME DOWN HERE.

166
00:06:54,682 --> 00:06:56,717
[ ZIP! ]

167
00:06:56,750 --> 00:06:59,086
OH, NO, NO,
NO, NO, NO, NO. NO.

168
00:06:59,119 --> 00:07:02,055
THE MODEL SHOULD BE
IN SOMETHING SIMPLE!

169
00:07:02,089 --> 00:07:04,692
SOMETHING INSPIRED BY...

170
00:07:04,725 --> 00:07:06,159
THE NATURE.

171
00:07:07,595 --> 00:07:10,030
THAT'S JUST
WHAT I WAS THINKING.

172
00:07:11,899 --> 00:07:13,601
UM, GIVE ME A MOMENT
AND I'LL, UH,

173
00:07:13,634 --> 00:07:15,068
PUT A LITTLE SOMETHING
TOGETHER.

174
00:07:15,102 --> 00:07:17,471
YES. THAT WILL NOT
BE NECESSARY.

175
00:07:17,505 --> 00:07:18,539
BUT -- BUT --

176
00:07:18,572 --> 00:07:21,875
HOW ARE YOU GOING TO HELP ME
"SHINE ACROSS EQUESTRIA"

177
00:07:21,909 --> 00:07:25,012
IF I DON'T DESIGN SOMETHING NEW
FOR THESE PICTURES?

178
00:07:25,045 --> 00:07:27,881
I AM NOT GOING TO HELP YOU
SHINE ACROSS EQUESTRIA!

179
00:07:27,915 --> 00:07:30,884
I AM GOING TO HELP
HER SHINE.

180
00:07:30,918 --> 00:07:33,153
SHE IS MY STAR!

181
00:07:33,186 --> 00:07:34,788
YOU, GO.

182
00:07:34,822 --> 00:07:36,824
[ GASPS ]

183
00:07:45,298 --> 00:07:47,100
I CAN'T, RARITY.

184
00:07:47,134 --> 00:07:49,169
OH, BUT YOU MUST,
FLUTTERSHY.

185
00:07:49,202 --> 00:07:51,705
PHOTO FINISH
WANTS TO MAKE YOU A STAR.

186
00:07:51,739 --> 00:07:54,107
THIS IS THE OPPORTUNITY
OF A LIFETIME.

187
00:07:54,141 --> 00:07:57,144
I KNOW WE WERE BOTH HOPING
IT WOULD BE MY LIFETIME,

188
00:07:57,177 --> 00:07:59,947
BUT NONETHELESS, YOU CAN'T
THROW AWAY THIS CHANCE.

189
00:07:59,980 --> 00:08:01,582
YOU MUST DO THIS
FOR ME.

190
00:08:01,615 --> 00:08:04,251
YOU MUST.
YOU MUST! YOU MUS-S-T!

191
00:08:04,284 --> 00:08:05,953
Photo Finish:
FLOOTTERSHY!

192
00:08:05,986 --> 00:08:08,088
IT IS TIME TO MAKE...

193
00:08:08,121 --> 00:08:10,090
THE MAGICS!

194
00:08:11,158 --> 00:08:12,526
[ TING! ]

195
00:08:14,261 --> 00:08:15,629
OH, WUNDERBAR!

196
00:08:15,663 --> 00:08:18,265
YOU ARE LIKE
A DELICATE FLOWER --

197
00:08:18,298 --> 00:08:21,569
SO MUCH MORE ALLURING WITHOUT
ALL THOSE SPARKLES AND FEATHERS.

198
00:08:21,602 --> 00:08:22,603
[ SIGHS ]

199
00:08:22,636 --> 00:08:24,171
[ SEWING MACHINE WHIRRING ]

200
00:08:27,975 --> 00:08:30,010
HOW'D IT GO?!
HOW'D IT GO?!

201
00:08:30,043 --> 00:08:32,245
IT DIDN'T.

202
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:35,783
PHOTO FINISH WANTED TO WORK
WITH FLUTTERSHY, NOT ME.

203
00:08:35,816 --> 00:08:37,918
OH, RARITY.
I'M SO SORRY.

204
00:08:37,951 --> 00:08:40,187
IS THERE ANYTHING
WE CAN DO?

205
00:08:40,220 --> 00:08:44,057
I JUST...VANT TO BE ALONE
RIGHT NOW.

206
00:08:45,693 --> 00:08:49,897
YOU HEARD HER.
SHE "VANTS TO BE ALONE."

207
00:08:49,930 --> 00:08:51,899
[ SPROING! SPROING! ]

208
00:08:51,932 --> 00:08:53,066
[ GASPS ]

209
00:08:53,100 --> 00:08:56,570
WHAT? I DIDN'T THINK
SHE MEANT ALONE ALONE.

210
00:08:57,905 --> 00:08:58,972
[ SNIFFS ]

211
00:09:02,075 --> 00:09:03,543
[ WINCES ]

212
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:08,882
TOO MUCH BLUSH.

213
00:09:08,916 --> 00:09:10,651
[ RATTLE! ]

214
00:09:10,684 --> 00:09:12,920
NOT ENOUGH.

215
00:09:12,953 --> 00:09:14,054
TOO MUCH.

216
00:09:14,087 --> 00:09:15,055
[ WINCES ]

217
00:09:15,088 --> 00:09:16,624
NOT ENOUGH.

218
00:09:18,125 --> 00:09:20,093
PERFECT.

219
00:09:20,127 --> 00:09:23,797
AH-AHHHHHH...

220
00:09:23,831 --> 00:09:24,798
choo!

221
00:09:24,832 --> 00:09:25,799
OH, YES!

222
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:28,802
EVEN HER SCHNEEZES
ARE GRACEFUL!

223
00:09:28,836 --> 00:09:29,937
NOW GO!

224
00:09:29,970 --> 00:09:31,204
[ ZIP! ]

225
00:09:31,238 --> 00:09:33,807
HOW DO YOU FEEL?
EXCITED? OVERJOYED?

226
00:09:33,841 --> 00:09:36,176
THRILLED BEYOND
YOUR WILDEST DREAMS?

227
00:09:36,209 --> 00:09:38,211
N-NERVOUS.

228
00:09:38,245 --> 00:09:39,880
NERVOUS?
DON'T BE RIDICULOUS!

229
00:09:39,913 --> 00:09:42,015
YOU'RE ONLY FACING
A LARGE CROWD OF PONIES

230
00:09:42,049 --> 00:09:45,052
WHO WILL BE WATCHING YOUR EVERY
MOVE AND SILENTLY JUDGING YOU.

231
00:09:45,085 --> 00:09:46,286
[ ELECTRONIC MUSIC PLAYS ]

232
00:09:46,319 --> 00:09:48,355
YOUR CUE! NOW GO!
[ YELPS ]

233
00:09:48,388 --> 00:09:50,090
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

234
00:09:50,123 --> 00:09:52,125
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

235
00:09:57,898 --> 00:10:01,368
I CAN'T LET RARITY DOWN.
I MUST DO THIS.

236
00:10:01,401 --> 00:10:04,738
MUST, MUST, MUST.

237
00:10:10,110 --> 00:10:12,846
[ CHEERING, HOOVES STOMPING ]

238
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:14,314
SO GRACEFUL.

239
00:10:14,347 --> 00:10:15,816
SO LOVELY.

240
00:10:15,849 --> 00:10:18,752
Pony: SO PERFECT
FOR MY NEW ADVERTISEMENT.

