250
00:11:03,263 --> 00:11:04,031
FLUTTERSHY!
OVER HERE!

251
00:11:04,064 --> 00:11:06,800
BEAUTIFUL, THANK YOU.
THANK YOU.

252
00:11:06,834 --> 00:11:07,835
COME HERE!

253
00:11:07,868 --> 00:11:10,838
RIGHT HERE, FLUTTERSHY!
OVER HERE!

254
00:11:10,871 --> 00:11:12,806
FLUTTERSHY!
THERE YOU ARE.

255
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:14,808
[ SEWING MACHINE WHIRRING ]

256
00:11:15,876 --> 00:11:17,277
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

257
00:11:17,310 --> 00:11:19,412
HEY, OVER HERE, FLUTTERSHY!
LOOK OVER HERE!

258
00:11:19,446 --> 00:11:21,448
FLUTTERSHY!
MORE PICTURES,
PLEASE.

259
00:11:21,481 --> 00:11:22,950
[ CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING ]

260
00:11:22,983 --> 00:11:26,887
WOW.
LOOK HOW POPULAR YOU ARE.

261
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:29,022
I'M SO EXCITED FOR YOU.

262
00:11:29,056 --> 00:11:32,726
YOU MUST BE
HAVING THE BEST TIME EVER.

263
00:11:32,760 --> 00:11:35,328
OH, YES.
BEST TIME EVER.

264
00:11:35,362 --> 00:11:37,731
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]
