FLOOTTERSHY!

265
00:11:37,765 --> 00:11:39,933
I HAVE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU
EVERYWHERE.

266
00:11:39,967 --> 00:11:41,835
WE HAVE THE THING
AT THE PLACE!

267
00:11:41,869 --> 00:11:44,171
I'LL SEE YOU AT THE SPA,
OUR USUAL TIME?

268
00:11:44,204 --> 00:11:45,038
OF COURSE!

269
00:11:45,072 --> 00:11:48,475
I CAN'T WAIT TO HEAR
ALL ABOUT THE...

270
00:11:48,508 --> 00:11:50,243
THING AT THE PLACE.

271
00:11:50,277 --> 00:11:52,145
[ GASPS ]

272
00:11:52,179 --> 00:11:53,380
[ GRUNTS ]

273
00:11:53,413 --> 00:11:56,516
I'M THE ONE WHO SHOULD BE MOBBED
BY STRANGERS WHEREVER I GO.

274
00:11:56,549 --> 00:11:57,918
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

275
00:11:59,119 --> 00:12:01,221
WELCOME
TO CAROUSEL BOUTIQUE!

276
00:12:01,254 --> 00:12:04,224
IS SHE STILL HERE?
WE HEARD FLUTTERSHY WAS HERE.

277
00:12:04,257 --> 00:12:06,093
SORRY.
YOU JUST MISSED HER.

278
00:12:06,126 --> 00:12:07,961
BUT YOU'RE
STILL IN LUCK.

279
00:12:07,995 --> 00:12:11,031
I'M HAVING A HUGE SALE
ON SOME OF MY BEST DESIGNS.

280
00:12:11,965 --> 00:12:13,767
AND YOU ARE?

281
00:12:13,801 --> 00:12:15,368
RARITY, OF COURSE.

282
00:12:15,402 --> 00:12:17,237
NEVER HEARD OF YOU.

283
00:12:17,270 --> 00:12:19,206
[ GROWLS ]

284
00:12:24,812 --> 00:12:28,548
OBVIOUSLY, I, PHOTO FINISH,
AM THRILLED TO HAVE FOUND HER.

285
00:12:28,581 --> 00:12:29,482
PHOTO FINISH?

286
00:12:29,516 --> 00:12:32,152
SHE'S A NATURAL
IN FRONT OF THE CAMERA.

287
00:12:32,185 --> 00:12:33,954
UM, PHOTO FINISH?

288
00:12:33,987 --> 00:12:35,889
I ONLY NEED
TO POINT AND SHOOT,

289
00:12:35,923 --> 00:12:36,890
AND I CAPTURE...

290
00:12:36,924 --> 00:12:37,891
THE MAGICS!

291
00:12:37,925 --> 00:12:40,060
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

292
00:12:40,093 --> 00:12:42,262
PHOTO FINISH,
I'M SO SORRY TO INTERRUPT.

293
00:12:42,295 --> 00:12:44,197
IT'S JUST
THAT I'M RUNNING LATE.

294
00:12:44,231 --> 00:12:46,333
[ GASPS ]
HOW COULD I HAVE FORGOTTEN?!

295
00:12:46,366 --> 00:12:48,535
YOUR APPEARANCE
AT THE BALLET OPENING --

296
00:12:48,568 --> 00:12:51,839
EVERYPONY WHO IS ANYPONY
WILL BE THERE!

297
00:12:51,872 --> 00:12:54,975
OH, ACTUALLY, I'M SUPPOSED TO BE
MEETING MY FRIEND --

298
00:12:55,008 --> 00:12:56,009
WE GO!

299
00:12:59,046 --> 00:12:59,947
[ GROANS ]

300
00:12:59,980 --> 00:13:02,082
MY HOOVES ARE GETTING
POSITIVELY PRUNE-Y,

301
00:13:02,115 --> 00:13:04,051
I'VE BEEN WAITING HERE
SO LONG.

302
00:13:05,418 --> 00:13:08,588
OBVIOUSLY, FLUTTERSHY'S JUST
TOO BUSY WITH HER NEW CAREER

303
00:13:08,621 --> 00:13:10,958
TO SPEND TIME
WITH HER BEST FRIEND.

304
00:13:10,991 --> 00:13:13,160
I'M SURE
SHE JUST GOT TIED UP.

305
00:13:13,193 --> 00:13:14,361
OF COURSE SHE DID.

306
00:13:14,394 --> 00:13:16,563
SHE'S A BIG, BRIGHT,
SHINING STAR.

307
00:13:16,596 --> 00:13:19,366
I WISH
THAT STAR WOULD BURN OUT!

308
00:13:19,399 --> 00:13:22,235
RARITY, FLUTTERSHY
IS YOUR FRIEND.

309
00:13:22,269 --> 00:13:23,303
I KNOW! I KNOW!

310
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:25,438
AND I SHOULD BE
HAPPY FOR HER,

311
00:13:25,472 --> 00:13:27,474
BUT INSTEAD,
I'M JUST...UNH...JEALOUS!

312
00:13:27,507 --> 00:13:30,310
OH, PLEASE PROMISE YOU WON'T
TELL HER I FEEL THIS WAY!

313
00:13:30,343 --> 00:13:33,180
PLEASE? PLEASE?
PLEASE, PLEASE, PLE-E-ASE?

314
00:13:33,213 --> 00:13:34,447
YOU HAVE MY WORD.

315
00:13:34,481 --> 00:13:38,418
LOSING A FRIEND'S TRUST IS THE
FASTEST WAY TO LOSE A FRIEND.

316
00:13:38,451 --> 00:13:39,452
FOREVER!

317
00:13:44,091 --> 00:13:47,227
WOW!
YOU LOOK GREAT!

318
00:13:47,260 --> 00:13:49,462
FLUTTERSHY MAY BE
THE ONE WHO'S FAMOUS,

319
00:13:49,496 --> 00:13:52,532
BUT THAT DOESN'T MEAN I HAVE TO
STOP LOOKING FABULOUS.

320
00:13:56,503 --> 00:13:59,940
RARITY,
I'M SO SORRY I'M --

321
00:13:59,973 --> 00:14:03,877
OH, NO.
SHE'S ALREADY GONE, ISN'T SHE?

322
00:14:03,911 --> 00:14:05,212
SORRY.

323
00:14:05,245 --> 00:14:07,214
OH, I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.

324
00:14:07,247 --> 00:14:10,383
I AM SO FRUSTRATED,
I COULD JUST SCREAM.

325
00:14:10,417 --> 00:14:12,519
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

326
00:14:12,552 --> 00:14:15,622
Aaaah...

327
00:14:15,655 --> 00:14:17,624
FEEL BETTER?

328
00:14:17,657 --> 00:14:19,927
[ SIGHS ] NO.

329
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:21,962
CAN I TELL YOU
SOMETHING?

330
00:14:21,995 --> 00:14:22,762
OF COURSE.

331
00:14:22,795 --> 00:14:25,398
YOU PROMISE
NOT TO TELL RARITY?

332
00:14:25,432 --> 00:14:26,466
I SWEAR.

333
00:14:26,499 --> 00:14:28,035
PINKIE PIE SWEAR?

334
00:14:28,068 --> 00:14:29,636
CROSS MY HEART
AND HOPE TO FLY.

335
00:14:29,669 --> 00:14:31,538
STICK A CUPCAKE
IN MY [SCREAMS]

336
00:14:34,274 --> 00:14:36,176
I DON'T LIKE
BEING A MODEL.

337
00:14:36,209 --> 00:14:38,011
NO, I HATE
BEING A MODEL.

338
00:14:38,045 --> 00:14:40,213
ALL THIS ATTENTION IS AWFUL,
JUST AWFUL!

339
00:14:40,247 --> 00:14:41,949
AND I'M ONLY DOING IT

340
00:14:41,982 --> 00:14:45,352
BECAUSE RARITY TOLD ME
I MUST, I MUST, I MUST.

341
00:14:45,385 --> 00:14:48,455
[ SIGHS ] I MUST.

342
00:14:48,488 --> 00:14:50,523
OH, REALLY?

343
00:14:50,557 --> 00:14:53,060
WELL...

344
00:14:53,093 --> 00:14:55,462
IF YOU WANT TO KNOW
THE TRUTH, RARITY --

345
00:14:55,495 --> 00:14:56,496
[ SPROING! ]

346
00:14:58,498 --> 00:14:59,967
[ ZIP! ]

347
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,668
W-WHAT WERE YOU
ABOUT TO SAY?

348
00:15:01,701 --> 00:15:04,271
Forever!

349
00:15:04,304 --> 00:15:05,638
NOTHING.

350
00:15:10,677 --> 00:15:11,878
I WAS JUST THINKING --

351
00:15:11,911 --> 00:15:16,116
IF YOU REALLY DON'T LIKE BEING
A MODEL, YOU COULD ALWAYS QUIT.

352
00:15:16,149 --> 00:15:18,518
OH, NO. I COULD NEVER
DO SUCH A THING.

353
00:15:18,551 --> 00:15:20,420
RARITY
WOULD BE DEVASTATED.

354
00:15:20,453 --> 00:15:21,955
BUT RARITY TOLD ME --

355
00:15:21,989 --> 00:15:23,356
[ POP! ]
[ GASPS ]

356
00:15:32,565 --> 00:15:35,302
MMM! JUICY!

357
00:15:35,335 --> 00:15:36,403
[ GROANS ]

358
00:15:36,436 --> 00:15:39,472
OH, IF ONLY ALL THESE PONIES
DIDN'T LIKE ME SO MUCH,

359
00:15:39,506 --> 00:15:42,542
PHOTO FINISH WOULDN'T
WANT ME TO MODEL ANYMORE.

360
00:15:42,575 --> 00:15:44,477
SHE'D FIND
SOMEPONY ELSE WITH...

361
00:15:44,511 --> 00:15:46,013
THE MAGIC.

362
00:15:46,046 --> 00:15:47,347
I GUESS YOU'RE RIGHT.

363
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,348
[ DING! ]

364
00:15:48,381 --> 00:15:49,682
YOU'RE RIGHT.

365
00:15:49,716 --> 00:15:52,252
YOU'RE RIGHT! YOU'RE RIGHT!
YOU'RE RIGHT!

366
00:15:52,285 --> 00:15:53,253
[ CROWD GASPS ]

367
00:15:53,286 --> 00:15:54,254
IT'S FLUTTERSHY!

368
00:15:54,287 --> 00:15:56,356
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

369
00:15:58,625 --> 00:15:59,792
DON'T YOU SEE?

370
00:15:59,826 --> 00:16:03,230
ON HER OWN, FLUTTERSHY COULD
NEVER DO SOMETHING UNATTRACTIVE.

371
00:16:03,263 --> 00:16:04,998
BUT IF I USE MY MAGIC
TO HELP HER

372
00:16:05,032 --> 00:16:07,367
DO SOMETHING UNATTRACTIVE
AT HER NEXT FASHION SHOW,

373
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:09,402
NO ONE WILL EVER
WANT HER TO MODEL AGAIN.

374
00:16:09,436 --> 00:16:11,638
AND IF FLUTTERSHY
NO LONGER HAS TO BE A MODEL,

375
00:16:11,671 --> 00:16:14,174
RARITY WILL NO LONGER
HAVE TO BE JEALOUS OF HER.

376
00:16:14,207 --> 00:16:16,409
AND I'LL NO LONGER
HAVE TO KEEP THEIR SECRETS!

377
00:16:16,443 --> 00:16:19,112
IT'S THE PERFECT PLAN!
YOU CAN'T TELL ANYONE ABOUT IT.

378
00:16:19,146 --> 00:16:21,514
PROMISE ME
YOU WON'T TELL ANYONE?!

379
00:16:21,548 --> 00:16:23,383
[ ZIP! ]

380
00:16:30,457 --> 00:16:33,426
SO, YOU DO PROMISE
OR YOU DON'T?

381
00:16:33,460 --> 00:16:34,494
UH, YES!

382
00:16:34,527 --> 00:16:37,064
OBVIOUSLY, THAT'S WHY
I ZIPPED MY MOUTH CLOSED,

383
00:16:37,097 --> 00:16:38,231
THEN LOCKED IT WITH A KEY,

384
00:16:38,265 --> 00:16:40,133
THEN DUG A HOLE,
THEN BURIED THE KEY,

385
00:16:40,167 --> 00:16:42,802
THEN BUILT A HOUSE ON TOP OF THE
HOLE WHERE I BURIED THE KEY,

386
00:16:42,835 --> 00:16:45,138
THEN MOVED INTO THE HOUSE
ON TOP OF THE HOLE!

387
00:16:45,172 --> 00:16:47,074
OBVIOUSLY.

388
00:16:47,107 --> 00:16:49,076
[ CROWD MURMURING ]

389
00:16:49,109 --> 00:16:51,278
[ ELECTRONIC MUSIC PLAYING ]

390
00:16:54,414 --> 00:16:57,084
YOU REALLY THINK
IT'LL WORK?

391
00:16:57,117 --> 00:16:58,718
THEY LOVE YOU
FOR BEING YOU,

392
00:16:58,751 --> 00:17:01,354
SO ALL I HAVE TO DO
IS MAKE YOU NOT BE YOU.

393
00:17:01,388 --> 00:17:02,555
JUST LEAVE IT TO ME.

394
00:17:11,398 --> 00:17:14,567
I GUESS IT'S TIME TO SEE
WHAT ALL THE FUSS IS ABOUT.

395
00:17:20,140 --> 00:17:22,309
[ TINKLING ]

396
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,711
[ RECORD SCRATCHES ]

397
00:17:24,744 --> 00:17:26,579
[ CROWD GASPS ]

398
00:17:26,613 --> 00:17:28,115
[ GASPS ]

399
00:17:28,148 --> 00:17:29,116
[ BOING! ]

400
00:17:29,149 --> 00:17:30,117
UHHH...

401
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:31,318
[ HONK! ]

402
00:17:31,351 --> 00:17:32,852
AAH!

403
00:17:32,885 --> 00:17:34,687
[ CROWD GASPS ]

404
00:17:35,755 --> 00:17:36,823
[ CROWD GASPS ]

405
00:17:40,493 --> 00:17:42,129
AAH!

406
00:17:42,162 --> 00:17:43,763
[ SQUEAK! SQUEAK! ]

407
00:17:43,796 --> 00:17:45,432
[ CROWD GASPS ]

408
00:17:48,901 --> 00:17:50,737
[ BARK! BARK! ]

409
00:17:51,804 --> 00:17:53,673
[ CROWD GASPS ]

410
00:17:53,706 --> 00:17:54,774
OH, NO.

411
00:17:54,807 --> 00:17:57,310
[ HEE-HAW! ]

412
00:17:57,344 --> 00:17:58,545
[ CROWD BOOING ]

413
00:17:58,578 --> 00:18:00,313
GET HER OFF THE STAGE!

414
00:18:00,347 --> 00:18:03,283
SHE'S AN EMBARRASSMENT
TO ALL THINGS FASHION!

415
00:18:03,316 --> 00:18:06,286
I, PHOTO FINISH,
HAVE MADE A TERRIBLE MISTAKE!

416
00:18:09,856 --> 00:18:12,392
Rarity:
BRAVO! I SAY, BRAVO!

417
00:18:12,425 --> 00:18:13,460
BRAVO?!

418
00:18:13,493 --> 00:18:17,230
WHO COULD POSSIBLY SAY BRAVO
TO THAT HORRID DISPLAY?

419
00:18:17,264 --> 00:18:19,832
[ RARITY STOMPING ]
SUCH ATTITUDE!
SUCH PIZZAZZ!

420
00:18:19,866 --> 00:18:22,469
SHE'S INVENTED AN ENTIRELY
NEW KIND OF MODELING!

421
00:18:22,502 --> 00:18:24,771
WHO IS SAYING
THESE THINGS?

422
00:18:24,804 --> 00:18:26,439
[ GASPS ] IT'S HER!

423
00:18:26,473 --> 00:18:29,442
THE UNICORN IN THE GORGEOUS CAPE
AND HEADDRESS.

424
00:18:29,476 --> 00:18:31,778
NOW, THAT IS A PONY
WHO CLEARLY KNOWS

425
00:18:31,811 --> 00:18:33,813
A THING OR TWO
ABOUT FASHION.

426
00:18:33,846 --> 00:18:37,917
WELL, IF THAT FABULOUS PONY
LIKES IT, THEN I DO, TOO!

427
00:18:37,950 --> 00:18:38,918
BRAVO!

428
00:18:38,951 --> 00:18:39,919
YES!

429
00:18:39,952 --> 00:18:41,854
[ CROWD CHEERS ]

430
00:18:47,927 --> 00:18:49,896
[ SIGHS ]

431
00:18:51,498 --> 00:18:54,667
THIS IS AWFUL.
JUST AWFUL.

432
00:18:54,701 --> 00:18:57,337
SOMEHOW I'VE BECOME
MORE POPULAR THAN EVER.

433
00:18:57,370 --> 00:19:00,940
OH, I'M JUST SO FRUSTRATED,
I COULD JUST KICK SOMETHING!

434
00:19:00,973 --> 00:19:03,510
[ GRUNTS GENTLY ]

435
00:19:03,543 --> 00:19:07,314
IF ONLY RARITY DIDN'T WANT ME
TO BE A MODEL SO BADLY.

436
00:19:07,347 --> 00:19:09,282
[ GROANS ]
BUT RARITY --

437
00:19:09,316 --> 00:19:10,283
[ POP! ]

438
00:19:10,317 --> 00:19:12,919
FLUTTERSHY!
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

439
00:19:12,952 --> 00:19:14,721
I'M GREAT.

440
00:19:14,754 --> 00:19:17,457
I'M A SUPER-FAMOUS
FASHION MODEL.

441
00:19:17,490 --> 00:19:19,492
WHY WOULDN'T I
BE GREAT?

442
00:19:19,526 --> 00:19:20,760
BECAUSE YOU HA--

443
00:19:21,794 --> 00:19:23,496
OUT THERE
ON THE RUNWAY,

444
00:19:23,530 --> 00:19:25,765
EVERYONE WAS
TURNING ON YOU, AND --

445
00:19:25,798 --> 00:19:28,868
OH, FLUTTERSHY,
IT'S SO AWFUL.

446
00:19:28,901 --> 00:19:30,670
I WANTED THEM TO.

447
00:19:30,703 --> 00:19:32,205
YOU DID?!

448
00:19:32,239 --> 00:19:35,275
OF COURSE SHE DID!
BECAUSE --

449
00:19:36,343 --> 00:19:37,310
I'M JEALOUS!

450
00:19:37,344 --> 00:19:38,778
I WANTED
ALL THE ATTENTION,

451
00:19:38,811 --> 00:19:40,647
AND INSTEAD,
IT WAS GOING TO YOU.

452
00:19:40,680 --> 00:19:43,483
I EVEN STARTED HOPING THAT
YOU WOULD DO SOMETHING SILLY

453
00:19:43,516 --> 00:19:45,518
SO YOUR MODELING CAREER
WOULD BE OVER.

454
00:19:45,552 --> 00:19:47,520
BUT THEN,
WHEN IT STARTED HAPPENING,

455
00:19:47,554 --> 00:19:48,655
ALL I COULD THINK WAS,

456
00:19:48,688 --> 00:19:50,490
"HOW COULD I
WANT YOU TO FAIL

457
00:19:50,523 --> 00:19:52,359
AT SOMETHING
YOU LOVE SO MUCH?"

458
00:19:52,392 --> 00:19:54,294
BUT FLUTTERSHY
DOESN'T --

459
00:19:54,327 --> 00:19:55,428
[ GRUNTS ]

460
00:19:56,729 --> 00:19:57,730
LOVE?

461
00:19:57,764 --> 00:20:00,567
OH, RARITY,
I HATE BEING A MODEL.

462
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:01,568
YOU DO?

463
00:20:01,601 --> 00:20:02,802
MORE THAN ANYTHING.

464
00:20:02,835 --> 00:20:04,937
THEN WHY
DID YOU KEEP DOING IT?

465
00:20:04,971 --> 00:20:07,574
I WAS AFRAID IF I QUIT,
YOU'D BE MAD AT ME

466
00:20:07,607 --> 00:20:10,410
FOR NOT WANTING TO
"SHINE ALL OVER EQUESTRIA."

467
00:20:10,443 --> 00:20:11,711
AND I THOUGHT
IF I TOLD YOU

468
00:20:11,744 --> 00:20:13,446
HOW JEALOUS I WAS
OF YOUR SUCCESS,

469
00:20:13,480 --> 00:20:15,248
YOU'D THINK
I WAS A TERRIBLE FRIEND.

470
00:20:15,282 --> 00:20:16,249
NEVER.

471
00:20:16,283 --> 00:20:17,384
ALL THIS TIME.

472
00:20:17,417 --> 00:20:20,019
IF WE JUST TOLD EACH OTHER
THE TRUTH.

473
00:20:20,052 --> 00:20:23,323
I PROMISE NEVER TO KEEP
MY FEELINGS A SECRET AGAIN.

474
00:20:23,356 --> 00:20:24,223
ME TOO.

475
00:20:24,257 --> 00:20:26,493
Both:
CROSS MY HEART AND HOPE TO FLY.

476
00:20:26,526 --> 00:20:27,827
STICK A CUPCAKE IN MY EYE.

477
00:20:27,860 --> 00:20:29,596
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

478
00:20:29,629 --> 00:20:31,564
YOU WERE BWILLIANT!
BWILLIANT!

479
00:20:31,598 --> 00:20:33,666
I'VE ALREADY GOT
SIX PHOTO SHOOTS

480
00:20:33,700 --> 00:20:35,535
LINED UP
FOR TOMORROW ALONE.

481
00:20:35,568 --> 00:20:36,969
I'M SORRY, PHOTO FINISH,

482
00:20:37,003 --> 00:20:40,340
BUT I DON'T THINK I'LL BE ABLE
TO MAKE ANY OF THEM.

483
00:20:40,373 --> 00:20:41,774
WHA-A-T?

484
00:20:41,808 --> 00:20:43,009
WE GO!
WE GO!

485
00:20:43,042 --> 00:20:45,812
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

486
00:20:45,845 --> 00:20:48,381
VHAT HAS JUST HAPPENED?

487
00:20:48,415 --> 00:20:49,382
[ POP! ]

488
00:20:49,416 --> 00:20:51,584
SPIKE HAS A CRUSH
ON RARITY!

489
00:20:51,618 --> 00:20:52,752
[ ZIP! ]

490
00:20:52,785 --> 00:20:55,755
[ SIGHS ]
AND YOU WERE DOING SO WELL.

491
00:20:55,788 --> 00:21:00,059
NOW, THIS IS A WONDERFUL WAY
TO SPEND AN AFTERNOON.

492
00:21:00,092 --> 00:21:01,694
ISN'T IT, THOUGH?

493
00:21:01,728 --> 00:21:03,463
DEAR PRINCESS CELESTIA,

494
00:21:03,496 --> 00:21:06,466
BEING A GOOD FRIEND MEANS
BEING ABLE TO KEEP A SECRET,

495
00:21:06,499 --> 00:21:07,967
BUT YOU SHOULD NEVER BE AFRAID

496
00:21:08,000 --> 00:21:10,670
TO SHARE YOUR TRUE FEELINGS
WITH A GOOD FRIEND.

497
00:21:10,703 --> 00:21:12,472
DID YOU GET ALL THAT,
SPIKE?

498
00:21:12,505 --> 00:21:14,574
NO, I DID NOT.

499
00:21:14,607 --> 00:21:16,509
I STILL CAN'T BELIEVE
YOU TOLD SOMEONE

500
00:21:16,543 --> 00:21:18,411
ABOUT MY SECRET FEELINGS
FOR RARITY!

501
00:21:18,445 --> 00:21:19,579
YOU'RE RIGHT.

502
00:21:19,612 --> 00:21:22,815
THAT WAS WRONG OF ME,
AND I'M VERY SORRY.

503
00:21:22,849 --> 00:21:24,617
APOLOGY ACCEPTED.

504
00:21:24,651 --> 00:21:27,620
NOW WILL YOU TAKE DOWN
MY LETTER TO PRINCESS CELESTIA?

505
00:21:27,654 --> 00:21:28,488
I WOULD LOVE TO,

506
00:21:28,521 --> 00:21:32,459
BUT I'M A LITTLE BUSY
AT THE MOMENT.

507
00:21:32,492 --> 00:21:35,495
[ SIGHS ]

